370
00:13:57,965 --> 00:14:01,167
- ♪ Figure out a 30-course menu ♪
- This is insane.

371
00:14:01,168 --> 00:14:02,802
♪ Find a guy to draw some pictures ♪

372
00:14:02,803 --> 00:14:04,304
♪ You're going to want plenty ♪

373
00:14:04,305 --> 00:14:06,172
