♪ And up on your head ♪

380
00:14:18,052 --> 00:14:19,252
♪ La, la, la, la, la, la ♪

381
00:14:19,253 --> 00:14:20,754
♪ Glowing right above your forehead ♪

382
00:14:20,755 --> 00:14:22,188
♪ La, la, la, la, la, la ♪

383
00:14:22,189 --> 00:14:24,124
♪ You will wear
this little present from me ♪

384
